Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡美麗的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為『美』才是至上的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnDFLiSong-Bd\fs24\b0}{\fad(400,0)}美麗而殘酷的詩人\N 美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師您的確很美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與您相比…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的不只是外表喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育中不是也有美麗的姿勢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一舉一動　談吐言行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為世界是可以分成兩邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的事物和醜陋的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真頭疼  我恐怕是屬於醜陋這一類的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又讓它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽也找薛定諤？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}薛定諤：出自薛定諤的貓<schrodinger's cat>是奧地利物理學家埃爾溫·薛定諤\N試圖證明量子力學在宏觀條件下的不完備性而提出的一個思想實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要給貓送死後文  怎麼送啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語言不通  叫了它也不會停下等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東碰西撞地追它  結果追到這種地方來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  為了追貓  從那一直追到這裡來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這貓還真有毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐電車也要花2個小時的路程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特快的話  是1小時48分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還不是2小時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你這麼不嚴謹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才無法完成定額
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的發送率可是百分之百的 NO.1 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跟笨蛋過不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像還是有點自知之明的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飼主老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那貓好像是對沒有孩子的老夫婦養的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  也就是說他們差不多同時去世的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說不定比較幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只留下一個是很殘酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初二同班的美川文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊　記得是很文靜的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的孩子居然會槍殺自己的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是因為那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的積怨一口氣爆發了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是煌的女兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她槍殺了父親對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  別說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnDFLiSong-Bd\fs21\b0}襲擊美川煌的犯人是獨生女的少女A（13）嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然作家的女兒都很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 美川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要槍殺自己父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}鷗之路  感覺還不錯！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為沒計劃性地亂找是找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你整整3天來都在沒計劃性的亂追
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是我們來動腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}可以預防生活習慣病糖尿病的烏龍茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}木天蓼: 木天蓼基原為獼猴桃科植物葛棗獼猴桃\N果實有毒 貓及貓科動物愛吃 易引起中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  說到貓自然不能不提木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點過於理論主義  不過是有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真苫  0923
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又沒有這個世界的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你難道想當小偷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永久性的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}止步  請確認左右方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止小偷行徑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是無奈之舉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見  所以無法手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}等…文伽  我頭昏啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}要壞了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}真的要死啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有造成致命傷的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  你肯定看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼找薛定諤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像千秋的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時都是報告說收信人不明  然後溜之大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追了3天的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜做小偷  你還真是熱心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  小姊們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的衣服是情侶裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  腹語術？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有一手的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的話  很快可以人氣飆升哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他們到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星探
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星探？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄生蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒中彩的馬票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光化學煙霧（公害）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禿子的腦袋上還用梳子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼裝完模型剩下的框架子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少看不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這只章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  正當防衛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　我說  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥…痛…痛…放開我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你這個…放過我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買木天蓼的錢到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊　能不能不拿我當武器使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早就一直在房間打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中學時的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天還問我名冊在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來呢  薛薛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是薛定諤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一隻貓  名字還那麼長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有你的年齡會增長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵差是從死者中挑選的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  保持死時的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要什麼都不說啦  告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是薛定諤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用趕它走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候連薛定諤都不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕…貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵　這下有好看的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  沒想到和夫是弟弟  千代之介才是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真澀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  在下夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是野島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學時的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  要？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然  什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香  你知道美川的聯繫方式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事  想聯繫她下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香和美川關係很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  覺得你是不是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線索之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個　要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和文歌  交往過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你老實回答  告訴你也可以喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點提示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「提示」？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你知道什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡文歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和美川…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我會保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  該告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「提示」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川的聯繫方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教務主任打電話時說的被我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯澤綜合醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「暫時住院一陣子  聯繫方式也轉到那邊」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師在電話裡跟別人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯澤綜合醫院…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌拒絕掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為文歌也是喜歡他的

Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你還是有可愛的地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然怕貓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買完木天蓼還有剩下的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經打開了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間接接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的啦  都是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是沒出現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算木天蓼的氣味會擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是有極限的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓氣味充滿這個鎮子可是很  很…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薛定諤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0825
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  別妨礙到我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡0609
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是3天前就開始追的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓給姊姊我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還姊姊　明明長不大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不同  永遠年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說永遠的洗衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是洗衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年後就是nice body
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}文伽的CV植田的確是nice body
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事可說不准
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人即使長成大人也沒發育的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是千秋你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  前面前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能否暫時保持不動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊有點情況啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬樹麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從醫院逃出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…又怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  出了點事故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊  醫院就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不能稱為不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  差不多到飛行時間極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拆毀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡  解除代號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0913
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖  沒事的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原來喜歡貓啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是我的幸運物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動會上拿下第一名時是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出差的爸爸提早回家時是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男朋友相遇時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想我跟他的美好時光正要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  才想長大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是  反正我已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  今天是你的幸運日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  回去了還有成堆的悔過書要寫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人生前居住的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這間房的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才到坐電車也要花2個小時才能到的這裡來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對老爺爺和老奶奶來說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有那隻貓是親人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那機器到明天才能動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就好好地告別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  你的家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他們『結束』了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能找到這呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次事件後  三年都未曾睜開眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「未曾睜開眼」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…到底是誰啊

