Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近在身邊而卻遠及天邊的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們的絕望是偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.38,0:23:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶喊


